'From Squeak3.8gamma of ''24 November 2004'' [latest update: #6643] on 11 April 2005 at 1:17:31 am'!"Change Set:		RemoveMultiCharDate:			11 April 2005Author:			Andreas RaabRemoves MultiCharacter"| old new |old := MultiCharacter allInstances.new := old collect:[:each| Character value: each asInteger].old elementsForwardIdentityTo: new.!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #MultiCharacter!